Author: so_crat_ic
Text: I dont want to stop eating forever. but its a good reminder that I dont need food /now/. Especially if you are having small meals of protein and veg throughout the day, as long as you are getting vitamins and hydration. Skipping a couple meals wont actually kill you.

Author: DavidFrumTheBlock
Text: > “Forever” is near  Not at my body fat percentage
